name: Cave Painting (15/08/2021 GENAI FIRST)
description: An artwork in the Cave Painting Series by the artist M Plummer-Fernández. Created and minted 15/08/2021. This cave is the first in the series combining Generative Art techniques I created in 2012-2015 with the AI system I coded for the caves. This piece marks a significant milestone in the direction of this project and builds upon nine years of work. The Cave Paintings are produced by a custom neural network system that projects visions onto imaginary caves in response to prompts chosen by the artist.
